title: Raiders vs Chiefs preview & Jets debacle
itunes:title: Raiders vs Chiefs preview & Jets debacle
description:
A room filled with heroes - Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler, Chris Wesseling,  & Gregg Rosenthal – recap the Monday night beat down the Colts gave the Jets at MetLife Stadium. Then, the heroes introduce a new game succinctly entitled “Hey, do you want be in my shoes? No thank you, I would rather be in some others” before diving into the Thursday night AFC West battle between the Raiders and the Chiefs. Plus, Conor Orr joins from New Jersey to get a few things off his chest.
